FT  05 APR 94 / Company News (This Week): Alcatel Alsthom - Other companies
The French telecommunications, engineering and transport group will announce
1993 results tomorrow. Mr Pierre Suard, chairman, has previously indicated
that net profits will be about the same as 1992, for which the company
reported FFr7.05bn (Pounds 800m).  He has also warned that difficult
conditions in some of the group's telecoms markets.
